#compdef embedmd
# Documentation: https://github.com/campoy/embedmd
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-17
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above.

# embedmd: embed code into markdown files (campoy/embedmd)
_arguments -s -S \
  '-w[rewrite file in place]' \
  '-d[show diff between current file and processed output]' \
  '*:markdown files:_files -g "*.md(-.)"'
